name: @kingjs/poset.encode
description: Encodes an adjacency list and vertex property map into a descriptor whose property names, when split on `$`, reveal a vertex name followed by its adjacent vertices, and whose property values correspond to vertex properties.
author: Chris King <kingces95@gmail.com>
